-- Redeem Tests

Test "Mint then Redeem All"
    NewComptroller
    ListedBToken WBTC bWBTC initialExchangeRate:0.1 tokenType:WBTC
    Prep Geoff 70e8 WBTC bWBTC
    Mint Geoff 50e8 bWBTC
    -- Check current affairs
    Assert Equal (Erc20 bWBTC TokenBalance Geoff) 500e8
    Assert Equal (Erc20 WBTC TokenBalance Geoff) 20e8
    -- Any other good invariants?
    Invariant Static (BToken bWBTC ExchangeRateStored)
    -- Now redeem after some time
    FastForward 2 Blocks
    RedeemUnderlying Geoff 50e8 bWBTC
    Assert Equal (Erc20 bWBTC TokenBalance Geoff) Zero
    Assert Equal (Erc20 WBTC TokenBalance Geoff) 70e8

