Test "Mint then Redeem Too Much"
    NewComptroller
    ListedBToken WBTC bWBTC initialExchangeRate:0.1 tokenType:WBTC
    Prep Geoff 70e8 WBTC bWBTC
    Mint Geoff 50e8 bWBTC
    Prep Jared 70e8 WBTC bWBTC
    Mint Jared 50e8 bWBTC
    -- Check and hold static
    Invariant Static (BToken bWBTC ExchangeRateStored)
    Invariant Remains (Erc20 bWBTC TokenBalance Geoff) 500e8
    Invariant Remains (Erc20 WBTC TokenBalance Geoff) 20e8
    -- Now redeem after some time
    FastForward 2 Blocks
    AllowFailures
    RedeemUnderlying Geoff 50.1e8 bWBTC
    Assert Revert "revert subtraction underflow"

